      "content": "i get that it's not ideal but i'm not talking about getting drunk lol, just a single glass of wine. i've heard that a little bit of alcohol actually helps sedative meds work more effectively by relaxing the system. is there really a big difference between a normal glass and taking the pill alone? i just really need to sleep tonight.",
